title: Babe of the Day—Marie Charlene
text:
Share on Twitter Model Mayhem 
Marie Charlene is about as bite-sized as models get, clocking in at just 5’1″ and 88 pounds.Marie’s diminutive size almost goes unnoticed, however, as the Austria-based model’s banging body tends to capture viewers full attentions. 
The 23-year-old is still relatively new to the industry but given her lustful, petite style, we’re confident Marie will have plenty of success. Marie is also a professional makeup artist, so she does it all herself. Yet another feather in the ole cap (or G-string). 
The model isn’t particularly active in social media, but you can still enjoy her below photos.
